## v0.2.6 - 2026-04-26



## 0.2.5 - 2026-04-25

- Bump version to 0.2.5; improvements: mirror health cache, parallel mirror probe, concurrent provider resolution, fix parsing and download-extension logic, CI release workflows and tests.

## 0.2.6 - 2026-04-26

- Hide provider download links in UI to avoid triggering anti-bot protections and 403s.
- Remove provider-page fetching and helper resolvers; expose no provider anchors by default.
- Increment version to 0.2.6 and update tests accordingly.

## Unreleased

 - Minor fixes and maintenance.
